sequenceDiagram
    participant V as Voter (Mobile)
    participant A as API Gateway
    participant S as Auth Service
    participant D as Database
    participant E as Email Service

    V->>A: Request OTP (RegNo)
    A->>S: Validate Voter
    S->>D: Check Eligibility
    D-->>S: Voter Eligible
    S->>E: Send OTP
    E-->>V: Email with OTP
    
    V->>A: Submit OTP
    A->>S: Verify OTP
    S->>D: Validate Hash
    D-->>S: Valid
    S->>D: Create Ballot Token
    S-->>V: Return Ballot Token
